Bonekickers 

Tue 5 Aug, 21:00 - 22:00 60 mins 

5/6. The Lines of War

A British World War One tank containing the remains of six bodies is uncovered in France and as evidence of a war crime emerges, an international feud with French and German archaeologists is ignited. Also in HD. Language may offend. [AD,S]
